du Sud

181
00:14:37.020 --> 00:14:39.150
Le bataillon du Sud de Denjiro.

182
00:14:39.820 --> 00:14:43.150
Ensemble, elles rassemblent
cinq mille soldats.

183
00:14:46.870 --> 00:14:50.040
Polar Tang

184
00:14:52.280 --> 00:14:54.040
Le submersible du pirate Law

185
00:14:54.040 --> 00:14:56.380
